data.description: This is a trust sale. Nestled in the heart of Jefferson Park, this charming 2-bedroom, 1-bathroom residence presents a unique opportunity for buyers and investors due to its trust sale status. Situated on a generous 5,503 square foot lot, this property offers boundless potential for an Accessory Dwelling Unit (ADU), making it a standout investment. Spanning 1,021 square feet, this home serves as a blank canvas, eagerly awaiting your creative vision. Inside, you'll find beautiful hardwood floors that exude an air of elegance, while the inclusion of a tankless water heater ensures both energy efficiency and on-demand hot water for your comfort. Also includes a covered patio in the rear with solar panels. With a convenient two-car garage, your parking and storage needs are well taken care of, and a lengthy driveway offers additional parking options for you and your guests. The location of this property is truly a gem, offering effortless access to the Expo Line for convenient transportation to Culver City, Santa Monica, West L.A., Beverly Hills, and Hollywood. A world of shopping, entertainment, and art galleries are at your doorstep, with renowned destinations such as Rodeo Drive, Beverly Center Mall, and world-class dining just a short distance away. Please note that this property is being sold in its as-is condition, and showings are subject to offer. For additional information and to seize this exceptional opportunity, reach out to Listing Agent 1 today. Don't miss the chance to transform this property into the masterpiece it can become. Your future in Jefferson Park awaits! Multiple offers above list price submit highest and best at this time. No blind offers or less than listing price will be considered.
